| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6258 — Recovery Inhibition (genesis)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7f64062f-7957-5d05-ab3a-cfc5e98bfbc4"
